; Names for each of the items in the menu. Names must be in quotes.
; Use "" or remove itemname parameter to disable an item. If all are disabled,
; goes straight to demo mode (hold Esc to quit demos).
;
; Ikemen feature: Flexible submenu grouping. General syntax for handling modes
; looks as follows: menu.itemname.optional_submenus.item = "displayed text"
; where:
; * optional_submenus: combination of 1 or more strings, separated by dots,
;   where each of them refers to additional level of nested menus. For example
;   menu.itemname.menuextras = "EXTRAS" means we're displaying EXTRAS option on
;   the screen (in this case right on the main menu) that opens up additional
;   submenu with items using menuextras as a prefix, e.g. 
;   menu.itemname.menuextras.freebattle
; * item: strings used to start modes and control menus. Following item names
;   are reserved by the engine:
;   - arcade: Arcade Mode
;   - versus: Versus Mode
;   - teamarcade: Team Arcade
;   - teamversus: Team Versus
;   - teamcoop: Team Cooperative
;   - survival: Survival
;   - survivalcoop: Survival Cooperative
;   - storymode: Story Mode (reserved, not implemented yet)
;   - timeattack: Time Attack
;   - training: Training Mode
;   - watch: Watch Mode
;   - options: Options
;   - exit: Exit the game
;   - back: Back to previous menu
;   - freebattle: Free Battle (Quick Match)
;   - timechallenge: Time Challenge
;   - scorechallenge: Score Challenge
;   - vs100kumite: VS 100 Kumite
;   - bossrush: Boss Rush
;   - trials: Trials Mode (reserved, not implemented yet)
;   - records: Overall score records (reserved, not implemented yet)
;   - ranking: Rankings/leaderboards data (reserved, not implemented yet)
;   - replay: Replay
;   - randomtest: Random AI Battles
;   - tournament32: Tournament Mode starting from round of 32 (reserved)
;   - tournament16: Tournament Mode starting from round of 16 (reserved)
;   - tournament8: Tournament Mode starting from quarterfinals (reserved)
;   - joinadd: New IP Address
;   - serverhost: Host Game
;   - serverjoin: Join Game (reserved submenu)
;   - connect: start items appended to serverjoin submenu (with 'ip_' prefix)
;   - server: special submenu, opened automatically by serverhost/serverjoin 
;   - netplayversus: Online Versus
;   - netplayteamcoop: Online Cooperative
;   - netplaysurvivalcoop: Online Survival
;   - bonusgames: Bonus Games (reserved submenu)
;   - bonus: start items appended to bonusgames submenu (with 'bonus_' prefix)
; Order in which menu items will show up on the screen depends on their order in
; screenpack DEF file. Submenus should be declared before parameters referring
; to items nested inside those menus. Itemnames added via external modules also
; work with this system.

